author: Sean Maher
title: Sean Maher
text: I had a great experience with this service. The agent McGowan was helpful and responsive to my emails. The hotels I requested Quote: s from also responded promptly (in contrast with another service that I used where most of the hotels did not respond to my request for a Quote: ).
